{"tid":1150108,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度將針對 Android 系統開展反壟斷調查","createTime":"2019-05-11T15:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T15:14:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6160953678b59893ccc0d6eefa6b98ab923ab69","tid":1150108,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"類似 Google 的大型企業，如果其產品規模和佔有率太高，容易觸犯反壟斷法。繼之前在歐盟被判大額罰款之後，有消息透露印度亦打算針對 Android 開展類似調查。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，印度競爭委員會認為 Google 有利用 Android 在市場上的佔有率優勢來阻礙競爭的嫌疑，因此去年開始已經收集資料準備正式展開調查，而全面調查已經在上月開始，但有關當局仍然未有正式公佈。印度競爭委員會去年已經因 Google 搜尋存在偏見，以及濫用市場地位，向 Google 罰款 1,950 萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n這個反壟斷調查與之前歐盟對 Google 罰款50 億美元的案件類似，當時歐盟判罰的原因是 Google 要求 Android 手機廠商安裝 Chrome 瀏覽器、Google 搜尋以及 Play Store，令 Google 不公平地獲得競爭優勢。Google 後來在歐盟讓用家選擇想要使用的瀏覽器和搜尋引擎。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Reuters<br />\n<br />\n﻿ &bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=9f820183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=098c149e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a><br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=7a1f2d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/05/11/india-orders-anti-trust-probe-of-google-for-alleged-android-abuse/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F05%2F11%2Findia-orders-anti-trust-probe-of-google-for-alleged-android-abuse%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=deb7a705\" target=\"_blank\">ht